Extension.name: makeCERequests
Extension.initParam:
Makes an internal request to specified content editor resource. Supports only 'edit', 'preview' and 'modify' commands only. Expects the input document to the request has the following format. <!ELEMENT ContentEditorItem(PSXParam+)> <!-- The format of resource is 'appName/ceDataSetName' --> <!ATTLIST ContentEditorItem Resource CDATA #REQUIRED> <!ELEMENT PSXParam(Value+)> <!ATTLIST PSXParam Name CDATA #REQUIRED> <!ELEMENT Value(#PCDATA>
Expects the minimum parameters required for content editor request, otherwise throws exception. Returns the result document with item content inserted or updated or queried.
<ContentEditorItem Resource='appName/ceDataSetName'> </ContentEditorItem>
